Name of eligible Cooperative that was utilized to execute the awarded contract.  Acronyms used in the data field stand for:  
HGAC = Houston Galveston Area Council; 
MMCAP = Minnesota Multistate Contracting Alliance for Pharmacy; 
NJPA = National Joint Powers Alliance; 
NVP = NASPOValuePoint; 
WSCA = Western States Contracting Alliance

A = State agency; 
S = School district; 
M = Municipality

Data Source of registered vendors in market that were outreached to for notification of solicitation.
GSA = US General Services Administration; 
SBA = US Small Business Administration; 
OSD = Office of Supplier Diversity; 
GSS = Government Support Services; 
Total = Total number of vendors outreached to for a specific solicitation
